title: Modern Flat in Prime Location near Wicker Park and Bucktown!
map_address: N Rockwell St near W Evergreen Ave
posting_body: ['*NOTE:', 'This home is currently occupied.', 'For the health and safety of our current residents, please email us to get more info.', 'OVERVIEW', 'This is a must see home!', 'Near Division Street, this home is around all the restaurants & shops that Wicker Park & Bucktown have to offer!', 'Enjoy the open floorplan featuring large windows, high ceilings, & hardwood floors throughout.', "You'll love the updated kitchen boasting stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a dishwasher, & a large bar/island.", 'Additional features include in-unit washer/dryer, central A/C & heat, & fantastic natural lighting.', 'Convenient access to public transportation with the Division, North, California & Western bus lines nearby.', 'Blue Line at Western is only about a 1 mile walk away, too!', 'All of the fun of Wicker Park & Bucktown within walking distance!', 'Earn these rent savings when you host short-term guests, with the help from our team at Loftium!', 'YOUR SPACE: 2 Beds, 1 Bath + Full Kitchen, Living Room and outdoor patio', 'GUEST SPACE: 1 Bed, 1 Bath + Separated and comes furnished!', 'Pet policy: pet rent of $30/month for one pet & $40/month for more than 1 pet', 'Please email me (Steph) for more information.']
